Setup PortAudio and PyAudio
1. Install Alsa Library, this bins PyAudio and PortAudio : $ sudo apt-get install libasound-dev
2. Download the latest stable version from http://www.portaudio.com/download.html
3. Extract the archive to /usr/src/
4. Execute the configure command and ensure that ALSA is set to 'yes': $ ./configure
5. Run : $ make
6. Run : $ make install
7. Run : $ ldconfig
8. Run : $ pip3 install pyaudio
